Pantyshot
[[Image:Najica-01.jpg|thumb|right|A fine example of the pantyshot from "Pantyshot: the Anime" aka Najica.]] 

[[Image:sometimesdudeshavepantyshots.jpg|thumb|right|[[Link mah boi|Link]] [[fangirls]] lurve male pantyshots.]]

[[Image:Attentionwhore-pantyshot.jpg|thumb|Who knew fat goth girls wore granny panties?]]

In common parlance, a photographic angle in movies, animations, or stills that allows the viewer a tantalizing glimpse of a woman's panty clad nether regions. Most frequently employed by the Japanese as panty covered coochie is slightly more erotic than pixelated muff. Aka: [[Haruhi|Haruhi]]

== In Anime ==
<gallery>
Image:Pokepantyshot.jpg|Cartoon Network endorsed.
Image:ITS A TRAP POKEMON26.jpg|[[doing it wrong|Another type of Pantyshot.]]
Image:Sonicxcreampantyshot.jpg|This would make any [[Chris-Chan|Sonic fag]] [[cream]] their pants.
</gallery>

When an anime series desperately needs to acquire or keep a fan base, it will often turn to the only thing it can do without crossing the [[hentai]] line: showing upskirt shots of prepubescent schoolgirls.

The pantyshot is usually seen when some [[16 year old girl|chick]] kicks a guy, then you see her panties. The next thing you know, your "[[wapanese|friend]]" and or "[[luser]]s" will start furiously masturbating.

Some call it "fan service", but we call it "desperate".

Too much gay doll pantyshots in ''Zatch Bell''.

== In Videogames ==
<gallery>
Image:Pantyshot-Linekillspirits.jpg|''Line-Kill Spirits'' brings the prepubescent pantyshot to gaming.
Image:Pantyshot-dead-or-alive-ultimate.jpg|The pantyshot game genre needs more elf costumes.
Image:Krystaliswearingathong.gif|Nintendo made [[Krystal]] wear a thong to please the [[furfag|fanboys]].
